summary: changes the dub of you're game to Japanese
descriptionHtml:
I know there are tones of tutorials to change the language of you're game but i thought I'd upload the files (Again) just to make it easier.

Requirements 
All DLC's but if you don't have any or one manually install it and pick witch ones you want.

Note
This only contains the .bsa files it dose not include the actual DLC's.

Side note
I've got a bunch of models from 3ds max if anyone wants them i might upload them to modders resources at some point but if you want to see before leave me a comment or pm me. also i have a patreon for some thing completely different from skyrim i can't link it because i got told off for it last time but it's a yuri visual novel come to my twitter @Atsuko_Soul if you're interested  

If you like this mod please endorse it and tell me what you like or dislike about playing skyrim in Japanese
author: darkarisen
